Package com.persistentsystems.socketclient.messaging

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WrJsonFirmwareMessageBuilder
    This is an (internal) class used to build an API compliant message for firmware uploads.
    WrJsonIperfMessageBuilder
    This is an (internal) class for build an API compliant Iperf message.
    WrJsonMessageBuilder
    This is an (internal) basic JSON message builder to build API compliant messages.
    WrJsonNetworkMessageBuilder
    This is an (internal) API compliant message builder to build network messages.
    WrMessageToken
    This is a simple data class to hold a few static functions for use with (internal) websocket messaging.
